==Translingual==

===Cardinal numeral===
'''II'''

# [[Roman numeral]] representing two ([[two|2]].)  In unicode it is represented by the symbol: [[Ⅱ]].

===Ordinal numeral===
'''II'''

# [[Roman numeral]] representing the [[second]], especially in the names of [[monarch]]s or [[pope]]s.  In unicode it is represented by the symbol: [[Ⅱ]].

